- Ordered sets classes:

  Span - An object representing a single span

  Set::Recurrence - An object representing a recurrence

  Set::Infinite - An object representing recurrences, multiple spans, etc.

  Set::Integer - A special case of Set::Infinite

- Functional versions of some of the above classes:

  Span::Functional

  Set::Functional::Recurrence

  Set::Functional::Infinite
